Multi-Threaded Directory Scanner.

dirscan scans website folder structure by using wordlist file. Most of pentesters
use this kind of tools to do information gathering on the target website. You can use
dirscan by passing word list and website list file to start scanning.

Quick build & install
========================
  - recent Linux system with all options, make and install :
    $ make -j $(nproc)
    $ ./src/dirscan --words wl.txt --sites sites.txt


Required dependencies
========================
  - CURL

On debian or Ubuntu systems and their derivatives, you may get curl
at once by issuing one of the following commands:
  $ sudo apt-get install libcurl4-openssl-dev
  or 
  $ sudo apt-get install libcurl4-nss-dev
  or
  $ sudo apt-get install libcurl4-gnutls-dev
